title: Number of lobbyists in the U.S. 2000 to 2019
summary: This is a line chart with an x axis representing Year and a y axis representing Number of lobbyists, containing a total of 20 data points.
Overall Number of lobbyists has decreased over the Year.
The most drastic increase took place within the Year 2004 and 2005.
Maximum Number of lobbyists, about 14825.0 was reported at Year 2007
The lowest Number of lobbyists, of value 11188.0 was reported at Year 2016
